# JavaScript Code Guidelines

## Project Structure

This project uses JavaScript for:
- **CLI Tools**: [cli.js](mdc:src/cli.js) - Command-line interface for deposits/withdrawals
- **Configuration**: [config.js](mdc:src/config.js) - Network and contract configurations
- **Demonstrations**: [minimal-demo.js](mdc:src/minimal-demo.js) - Example usage
- **Deployment**: [deploy.js](mdc:deploy.js) - Contract deployment script

## Key Libraries

- **Truffle**: Smart contract development framework
- **Web3.js**: Ethereum JavaScript API
- **Circomlib**: Circom circuit library for zk-proofs
- **snarkjs**: JavaScript implementation of zk-SNARKs

## Testing Framework

- Uses Mocha/Chai for testing
- Tests are in the `test/` directory
- Integration tests for contract functionality
- Mock contracts in [contracts/Mocks/](mdc:contracts/Mocks/)

## Build Scripts

- **Hasher Compilation**: [compileHasher.js](mdc:scripts/compileHasher.js) - Compiles Poseidon hasher
- **Key Download**: [downloadKeys.js](mdc:scripts/downloadKeys.js) - Downloads proving/verification keys
- **Ganache Helper**: [ganacheHelper.js](mdc:scripts/ganacheHelper.js) - Local development utilities

## Migration Scripts

Truffle migrations in `migrations/` directory:
- [2_deploy_hasher.js](mdc:migrations/2_deploy_hasher.js)
- [3_deploy_verifier.js](mdc:migrations/3_deploy_verifier.js)
- [4_deploy_eth_tornado.js](mdc:migrations/4_deploy_eth_tornado.js)
- [5_deploy_erc20_tornado.js](mdc:migrations/5_deploy_erc20_tornado.js)
